🧠 AI Chatbot for SQL Database Interaction
This project is an AI-powered chatbot designed to interact with SQL databases using natural language. Built with Langchain, Groq API, and Streamlit, it enables users to query databases without writing a single line of SQL—just ask questions in plain English!

🚀 Features
🔍 Natural Language to SQL: Convert human questions to accurate SQL queries using LLMs.

📊 Database Integration: Connects to various SQL databases (e.g., SQLite, MySQL).

🖥️ Streamlit Interface: Easy-to-use web interface for chatting and viewing results.

⚡ Powered by Groq API: Fast and efficient language model performance.

🛠️ Tech Stack
Python

Langchain

Groq API

Streamlit

SQLite/MySQL (any SQL database)

